# Adapter service

Adapter service is a part of IntroSDE final project 2016. It calls external API
from Forismatic.com and obtains motivational quotes, that are later used by users
to motivate themselves on their way towards fitness.

## Questions Collection [/questions]

### List All Questions [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

